Name: GAG
About the game: GAG is an interactive, dialogue-based psychological horror drama following the adventures of New York comedian Andy Barr and friends. Contains references to sexual abuse. The Steam edition also includes downloads for the previously-released short-form games BOX , CRASH , and FLUE .
